description: Lists map resources in your Amazon Web Services account.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: An optional limit for the number of resources returned in a single call. Default value: 100

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The pagination token specifying which page of results to return in the response. If no token is provided, the default page is the first page. Default value: null.

nested_items.name: Entries
nested_items.description: Contains a list of maps in your Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: MapName
nested_items.description: The name of the associated map resource.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: The description for the map resource.

nested_items.name: DataSource
nested_items.description: Specifies the data provider for the associated map tiles.

nested_items.name: PricingPlan
nested_items.description: No longer used. Always returns RequestBasedUsage.

nested_items.name: CreateTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp for when the map resource was created in ISO 8601 format: YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sssZ.

nested_items.name: UpdateTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp for when the map resource was last updated in ISO 8601 format: YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sssZ.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A pagination token indicating there are additional pages available. You can use the token in a following request to fetch the next set of results.
